<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340743' id='t-340743'>a kind of androgynous thing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='342655' id='t-342655'>I'll take you quickly through these works,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='345568' id='t-345568'>because I can't explain them for too long.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='348449' id='t-348449'>There are the layers,
