<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='398412' id='t-398412'>a garden.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='400132' id='t-400132'>We shake this box up,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='401553' id='t-401553'>and all these people kind of start
